{"type": "article", "id": 2191, "title": "J. Crew联名伸缩手袋", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T20:33:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222247qicdkf4CGu6Wsoam.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">即将来临的秋季，又到了寻觅搭配西装和风衣、同时满足通勤需求的手袋的时候了。来自加拿大蒙特利尔的知名箱包品牌 WANT Les Essentiels de la Vie 联手美国时尚品牌 J.Crew 推出的这款可伸缩 TWO-WAY TOTE 手袋就同时满足了时尚和功能性的两大需求。可伸缩的设计让它能在手持公文包和托特手袋之间轻松转换。丰富的色彩非常适合搭配印花西服。</span><a href=\"https://www.jcrew.com/womens_category/handbags/jcrewingoodcompany/PRD~A8665/A8665.jsp?Nbrd=J&amp;Nloc=en_US&amp;Nrpp=48&amp;Npge=1&amp;Ntrm=WANT+LES+ESSENTIELS+DE+LA+VIE&amp;isSaleItem=true&amp;color_name=NAVY%20WHITE%20STRIPE&amp;isFromSearch=true&amp;isNewSearch=true&amp;hash=row0\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222245ubknN9RJE6ZU3Dyh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49821429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222246BYrN1CoXGxcpOjSI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.246875\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222247rOboI1BqSMwJjgzE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}